---
At the end of each coding session:

1. Run the complete test suite:
   ```bash
   bin/rails test:all
   ```

2. Run RuboCop with GitHub format and auto correct:
   ```bash
   bundle exec rubocop --format github --autocorrect-all
   ```

This must be done:
- Before committing changes
- At the end of each coding session
- After completing or fixing a feature
- Before closing the project

No changes should be considered complete until all tests pass and RuboCop shows no offenses. That is for any code in the Rails application!
